The paper proposes a novel module for an embodied agent to enhance its mental imagery function, and a deep reinforcement framework for training. The paper involves topics such as artificial intelligence, robotics, computer vision, and natural language processing, which are all related to the sub-categories of cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, and cs.CL.
